1
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:58,480
I think Dearest must have her reasons

2
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,760
How could she marry into the Wang Family

3
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:01,680
There's a ghost

4
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:03,280
Did you see that? It flew right past

5
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,560
Right there, in a flash

6
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,680
There really is a ghost

7
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,080
There are no ghosts in this world

8
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,400
Y-you wait a second

9
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,760
This is safer

10
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,080
There's a silver dollar on the ground

11
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,560
Where? Where?

12
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,000
Where? Where? Where? Where?

13
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,640
Where is it? The silver dollar

14
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,320
Stay here and keep watch for me

15
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,640
That was exactly my thought

16
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,680
Three years ago, my sister married into the Wang Family

17
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,520
But she died for no clear reason

18
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,160
Rumor says the Wang Family is raising ghosts

19
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,520
No matter what dangers the Wang Family hides

20
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,440
I'll seek justice for my sister

21
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,760
Master, is that you?

22
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,600
Why is it you?

23
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:12,640
I imagined you in a wedding dress countless times

24
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,920
But never thought you'd wear it for another man

25
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,920
Today is my wedding day

26
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,320
If you know what's good for you, leave now

27
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,440
Or I'll call someone

28
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,560
Go ahead, call them

29
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,080
I am now a Concubine of the Wang Family

30
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,640
There's no possibility for us anymore

31
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,440
You filthy Bone-picker

32
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:33,080
You couldn't even afford 200 silver dollars in bride price

33
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,280
And you still wanted to marry my daughter

34
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,120
Dream on

35
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,000
Go, go, go, Mother, how unlucky

36
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,200
Get out of here

37
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,200
Back then, my master

38
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,800
took the Wang Family job to raise my bride price

39
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:51,120
And because of it, he died a wrongful death

40
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:54,360
Still worrying about the Zhao family's bride price?

41
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:57,080
Don't worry. I just took a big Wang Family job

42
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,240
Your bride price money will be no problem

43
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,760
And you

44
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,400
yet felt perfectly at ease

45
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,160
marrying into the Wang Family I hate most

46
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:07,960
Zheng Yu

47
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,000
You're hurting me

48
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,760
If Wang Shengchang comes in

49
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,520
and sees his new Fifth Concubine

50
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,800
having an affair with a filthy Bone-picker

51
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,320
What do you think he'll do?

52
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,800
Let go

53
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,880
About your master

54
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,120
I'm sorry

55
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,480
You can't stay here. Go now

56
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,440
The recent Severed Hand Murders

57
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,960
have everything to do with the Wang Family

58
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,760
If you don't want to die, come with me now

59
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,320
I'm not going

60
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,680
Don't be afraid, Xu Nan

61
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,240
Zheng Yu

62
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,000
What did you say?

63
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:47,120
I saw a man in Fifth Concubine's room myself

64
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,320
Catch him for me

65
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,640
Did you see clearly who it was?

66
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,520
Zheng Yu, hurry and go

67
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,040
No, no

68
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,400
I only saw his back

69
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,360
All the Wang Family's previous concubines died

70
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,720
Do you think that's a coincidence?

71
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,600
If you stay here, there's only death for you

72
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,320
Come with me

73
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,640
I am now the Wang Family's Fifth Concubine

74
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,720
I will not go with you

75
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,240
You have to come with me

76
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,400
I said I'm not going

77
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,400
Master! Master!

78
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,040
There's a vicious spirit in my room

79
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,360
Don't be afraid, don't be afraid

80
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,520
You got quite a fright

81
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,000
Master

82
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,000
Master, I'm scared

83
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,320
A petty thief must have snuck in

84
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,360
Hurry and check

85
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,600
Don't let that brat get away

86
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,680
Yes, Master. Go, hurry

87
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:50,880
Such huge footprints

88
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:57,440
What kind of monster is that thing?

89
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,320
Shuang'er has come to claim a life

90
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,760
Shuang'er! Shuang'er!

91
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,640
It must be Shuang'er

92
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,160
Shuang'er, spare my life

93
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,480
It had nothing to do with me

94
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,840
Master, the sound came from over there

95
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,120
One arm is missing

96
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,040
Shuang'er

97
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,960
Who? No, it wasn't

98
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,720
You scared me to death

99
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,040
Where's Dearest?

100
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:41,720
Didn't you catch it?

101
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,600
That scream just now...

102
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,840
I thought you'd been caught and beaten.

103
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,600
There's another victim in the Severed Hand Murders.

104
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,160
This kind of force doesn't seem human.

105
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,240
Xu Nan and I were even attacked by something.

106
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,800
Too bad I couldn't see what it was.

107
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,960
The Wang Family may truly have something unclean.

108
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,600
That was a ghost.

109
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,960
Don't come for me.

110
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:57,560
Don't come for me.

111
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,520
Don't come for me.

112
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,600
Master, I heard someone died.

113
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:10,240
I saw a man in Fifth Concubine's room.

114
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,400
Master

115
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,360
Master, what are you doing?
